<canvas class="output_canvas" id="output_canvas" width="1280" height="720" style="position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px;"></canvas>
<script type="module">
import {
    PoseLandmarker,
    FilesetResolver,
    DrawingUtils
} from "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/tasks-vision@0.10.0";

function calculateCentroid(landmarks) {
    if (!landmarks) 
      return [0,0,0];
    let validLandmarksCount = 0;
    const sum = landmarks.reduce((acc, landmark) => {
        if (landmark.x < 0 || landmark.x > 1 || landmark.y < 0 || landmark.y > 1)
            return acc;
        acc[0] += landmark.x;
        acc[1] += landmark.y;
        acc[2] += landmark.z;
        validLandmarksCount++;
        return acc;
    }, [0, 0, 0]);
    return validLandmarksCount > 0 ? sum.map(coord => coord / validLandmarksCount) : [0,0,0];
}

const vision = await FilesetResolver.forVisionTasks(
    "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/tasks-vision@0.10.0/wasm"
);

const poseLandmarker = await PoseLandmarker.createFromOptions(vision, {
    baseOptions: {
        modelAssetPath: `https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-models/pose_landmarker/pose_landmarker_lite/float16/1/pose_landmarker_lite.task`,
        delegate: "GPU"
    },
    runningMode: 'VIDEO',
    numPoses: 1
});

const peerId = "hhyhpnanki";
const video = document.getElementById("peerjs");
const canvasElement = document.getElementById("output_canvas");
const canvasCtx = canvasElement.getContext("2d");
const drawingUtils = new DrawingUtils(canvasCtx);
const videoHeight = "360px";
const videoWidth = "480px";
let lastVideoTime = -1;
async function predictWebcam() {
    canvasElement.style.height = videoHeight;
    video.style.height = videoHeight;
    canvasElement.style.width = videoWidth;
    video.style.width = videoWidth;
    let startTimeMs = performance.now();
    if (lastVideoTime !== video.currentTime) {
        lastVideoTime = video.currentTime;
        poseLandmarker.detectForVideo(video, startTimeMs, (result) => {
            canvasCtx.save();
            canvasCtx.clearRect(0, 0, canvasElement.width, canvasElement.height);
            const isThereSomePose = result.landmarks.length > 0;
            if (isThereSomePose) {
               const [x,y,z] = calculateCentroid(result.landmarks[0]);
               const vcentroid = [x*canvasElement.width,y*canvasElement.height];
               canvasCtx.beginPath();
               canvasCtx.arc(vcentroid[0], vcentroid[1], 5, 0, 2*Math.PI, true);
               canvasCtx.fill();
            }
            canvasCtx.restore();
        });
    }
    window.requestAnimationFrame(predictWebcam);
}

const stream = await navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia({
    video: true,
    audio: false
});
peer.call(peerId, stream).on('stream', peerStream => video.srcObject = peerStream);
video.addEventListener("loadeddata", predictWebcam);
</script>

<canvas class="output_canvas" id="output_canvas" width="1280" height="720" style="position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px;"></canvas>
<script type="module">
import {
    PoseLandmarker,
    FilesetResolver,
    DrawingUtils
} from "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/tasks-vision@0.10.0";

function calculateCentroid(landmarks) {
    if (!landmarks) 
      return [0,0,0];
    let validLandmarksCount = 0;
    const sum = landmarks.reduce((acc, landmark) => {
        if (landmark.x < 0 || landmark.x > 1 || landmark.y < 0 || landmark.y > 1)
            return acc;
        acc[0] += landmark.x;
        acc[1] += landmark.y;
        acc[2] += landmark.z;
        validLandmarksCount++;
        return acc;
    }, [0, 0, 0]);
    return validLandmarksCount > 0 ? sum.map(coord => coord / validLandmarksCount) : [0,0,0];
}

const vision = await FilesetResolver.forVisionTasks(
    "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/tasks-vision@0.10.0/wasm"
);

const poseLandmarker = await PoseLandmarker.createFromOptions(vision, {
    baseOptions: {
        modelAssetPath: `https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-models/pose_landmarker/pose_landmarker_lite/float16/1/pose_landmarker_lite.task`,
        delegate: "GPU"
    },
    runningMode: 'VIDEO',
    numPoses: 1
});

const peerId = "hhyhpnanki";
const video = document.getElementById("peerjs");
const canvasElement = document.getElementById("output_canvas");
const canvasCtx = canvasElement.getContext("2d");
const drawingUtils = new DrawingUtils(canvasCtx);
const videoHeight = "360px";
const videoWidth = "480px";
let lastVideoTime = -1;
async function predictWebcam() {
    canvasElement.style.height = videoHeight;
    video.style.height = videoHeight;
    canvasElement.style.width = videoWidth;
    video.style.width = videoWidth;
    let startTimeMs = performance.now();
    if (lastVideoTime !== video.currentTime) {
        lastVideoTime = video.currentTime;
        poseLandmarker.detectForVideo(video, startTimeMs, (result) => {
            canvasCtx.save();
            canvasCtx.clearRect(0, 0, canvasElement.width, canvasElement.height);
            const isThereSomePose = result.landmarks.length > 0;
            if (isThereSomePose) {
               const [x,y,z] = calculateCentroid(result.landmarks[0]);
               const vcentroid = [x*canvasElement.width,y*canvasElement.height];
               canvasCtx.beginPath();
               canvasCtx.arc(vcentroid[0], vcentroid[1], 5, 0, 2*Math.PI, true);
               canvasCtx.fill();
            }
            canvasCtx.restore();
        });
    }
    window.requestAnimationFrame(predictWebcam);
}

const stream = await navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia({
    video: true,
    audio: false
});
peer.call(peerId, stream).on('stream', peerStream => video.srcObject = peerStream);
video.addEventListener("loadeddata", predictWebcam);
</script>
